item.title: CVE-2023-34115|2023-06-13T18:50:33.223Z -- zoom%20video%20communications%2C%20inc. -- zoom%20meeting%20sdk
item.description: Buffer copy without checking size of input in Zoom Meeting SDK before 5.13.0 may allow an authenticated user to potentially enable a denial of service via local access. This issue may result in the Zoom Meeting SDK to crash and need to be restarted.
